# Root-level .dockerignore for Railway builds (build context = repo root)
# Prevents node_modules, build artifacts and secrets from being sent to the Docker daemon

**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/build
**/out
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.log
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output

# OS / IDE
.DS_Store
.idea
.vscode
